Deferred

## Context

OpenAPI specification tooling was considered but not enabled.
This project uses `api_style: {{ api_style }}` which
{% if api_style == "graphql" %}
uses GraphQL instead of REST, so OpenAPI tooling is not applicable.
{% else %}
could benefit from OpenAPI tooling but it was not enabled.
{% endif %}

## Decision

OpenAPI tooling is not included. To enable:
1. Set `api_style: rest` or `api_style: both`
2. Set `use_openspec: true`
3. Regenerate the project

## Consequences

Manual OpenAPI spec management is required.
